I have always been passionate about combining the real and digital worlds to create technology that transforms the everyday, and I envision myself contributing my talent to furthering Siemens' mission of enabling sustainable progress through technology. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

